::Battera::
She stayed on the cave ceiling, wrapped in her wings, hanging in the 
dark.  She finally started to look around.  It was a nice cozzy 
little cave.  it had warm air currents and a small stream running 
along the bottom.  She smiled and thought,finally, peace and quiet.
